# Git push policy

This project is linked to `git@github.com:Sussy-Designer/my-repo.git`.

After completing a build, feature, or meaningful set of changes:

1. Stage and commit with a clear message describing what was built or changed.
2. Push to `origin` on the current branch (prefer `main`).
3. Do not commit secrets, credentials, or `.env` files.

If push fails, report the error and retry once after checking auth with `gh auth status`.
